    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK899">
<l>ēntiya koḷkaiyār cīṟi ṉiṭaimurintu</l>
<l>vēntaṉum vēntu keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If those of exalted vows burst in a rage, even (Indra) the king will suffer a sudden loss and be entirely ruined.</l>
            </lg>
